Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915/opregion: check port number bounds for SWSCI display power state
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: ea958422291de248b9e2eaaeea36004e84b64043
Patch-mainline: v5.17-rc5
Alt-commit: 24a644ebbfd3b13cda702f98907f9dd123e34bf9
